Mashed potatoes are a speedy and effortless dish that can be made in the comfort of your home with simple ingredients. They can be paired with beef, chicken, fish, or veggies, depending on your preference. Ingredients  Preparation Step 1 After you have boiled the potatoes until soft, rinse them with cold water before transferring to a clean sufuria Step 2 Add milk, salt, butter and black pepper in the sufuria. Step 3 Mash until completely smooth. Season to taste. Then serve with your favourite dish. Enjoy with friends and family